a:15:{i:0;a:10:{s:2:"id";i:649;s:3:"uid";i:79;s:5:"title";s:50:"《全境封锁 2》全技能介绍与使用心得";s:7:"content";s:50462:"<p><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 在《全境封锁 2》游戏中有着各种各样的技能，包括辅助无人机、机枪塔、脉冲等等共计 8 个类别，每类型的第一个分支需要 1 点技能点，继续其他分支则需要 5 个「国土战略局装备」—— 注意不是技能点，是地图上开箱子能找到那个加专精的点数。技能点数可以在主线任务中获取，专精则是扫图开箱做任务。以下是全部技能详细介绍与心得体会。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><img src="https://p.qpic.cn/mwegame/0/6eeb3d8bf1beb9af95da0577b397ca18/"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">无人机</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);"><br/></strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">前锋：能够自动追踪目标，并在持续攻击过程中让目标维持在视线范围内；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">守卫：守卫无人机会使用装在无人机下方的声波发射器来让即将到来的子弹偏离；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">轰击：轰击无人机需要玩家指定两个地点，接着会在两点之间部署微型炸弹；<br/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">修补：修补无人机可以修复附近友军的装甲，也可以手动选择特定友军作为目标。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">心得：「修补」无人机能召唤一个持续加血的小玩意，对单刷的独狼比较有用，关键时刻能救命。「守卫」无人机则是提供类似防护罩的东西，被大哥的火力压制时可以缓解压力，关键是不用担心被打爆，因为坠毁后的无人机冷却时间只有平时的 1/4（约 15 秒），可迅速恢复。具体怎么选择，看个人爱好了。修补技能的替代其实还有不少（比如化学喷雾），所以可以考虑优先守卫。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><img src="https://p.qpic.cn/mwegame/0/7d33ecf0ef8e4af3a694e4c8711d430f/"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">脉冲</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">扫描：可以扫描周围区域的敌人，并标注在特工的抬头显示器上；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">遥控：遥控会部署在某个地点，会持续扫描周围区域的敌人，并标注在特工的抬头显示器上；<br/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">干扰：干扰会向外发出脉冲，让敌人的电子装备过载而无法使用；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">心得：初期不建议点开，冷却时间大约两分钟，和其他技能比起来性价比不高。经常组队的话可以考虑开一个扫描，视野是全队伍共享的。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><img src="https://p.qpic.cn/mwegame/0/70b7f53fc77b553bf0764674d205a45c/"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">机枪塔</strong><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">突击：可以自动追踪并攻击敌方目标，也可以手动调整追踪特定敌人；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">焚烧：由负责部署的玩家手动控制，火焰会以向前的锥状喷发；<br/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">狙击：狙击枪塔能对手动选定的目标发射大口径子弹。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Heiti SC&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">心得：可以考虑作为首发技能，「突击」是扔出一个自动机炮持续射击，适合单刷，射程很远而且能手动指定目标；「焚烧」是近距离大范围喷火，堵门用比较方便；「狙击」不太推荐，虽然威力大但射速很低，需要手动控制，而且经常射到墙上。顺便，机枪冷却比较长，架起来之后如果不再需要可以走过去长按对应按键收回，会减少很多冷却时间。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&qu